General.Name: Webstar Technology Group Inc
General.Description: Webstar Technology Group, Inc. provides software solutions. The company offers Gigabyte Slayer, a mobile application that enables users to transmit enhanced data over existing data streams to optimize data usage across mobile devices, including smartphones and tablets. It also provides WARP-G, a business-to-business software solution. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in St. Augustine, Florida.
